# 20 - Language Translator with Context
# Translate with cultural/contextual awareness

NAME translator
INPUT source_file
INPUT target_language
INPUT context DEFAULT "general"

GOAL read "Read content from $source_file."
GOAL analyze "Note key terms and tone for $context. Brief analysis only."
GOAL translate "Translate to $target_language. Preserve meaning and tone."
GOAL review "Quick accuracy check. Fix obvious errors only."

RUN translate USING read, analyze, translate, review
